AWS Code Star

>> Aws Console -> AWS CodeStar -> Create Project

>> Create Service Role -> Select Python as Template

>> Add Project Details -> Name - MyProject & ID

>> Project Repo -> Select GitHub -> Generate connection with GitHub -> Connect to GitHub -> Authorize AWS Connector to GitHub -> Install new app & connect -> Create Project

>> AWS will provision the resources for the Project -> Repo will all the req files will be created in GitHub

>> MyProject -> Pipeline: Source(Application Source) ->Build(PackageExport) ->Deploy(GenerateChangeSet->ExchangeChangeSet)